    <h2 class="small">Core Values in System Development</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>
        <h3 class="small">Sustainable IT Solutions</h3>
        <p>Embrace a sustainable future with our commitment to sustainable solutions. From investing in sustainable infrastructure to striving for enhanced efficiency in products and services, we influence clients towards sustainable choices, minimizing our carbon impact.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3 class="small">Accessibility in Our Solutions</h3>
        <p>Prioritizing inclusivity, our solutions adhere to the highest standards, complying with WCAG 2.0. We champion accessibility across all solutions, ensuring a seamless and equal digital experience for every user.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3 class="small">Privacy</h3>
        <p>Upholding the pillars of data ethics, our commitment to privacy includes the right to forget, digital consent, and robust privacy and security measures. With a keen focus on safeguarding sensitive information, we ensure trust and confidentiality in every interaction.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3 class="small">Knowledge Sharing with the Community</h3>
        <p>A commitment to the community extends beyond technology. We actively share knowledge and insights, promoting collaboration, innovation, and the collective growth of our shared digital landscape, driven by open-source principles.</p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </article>
